  "title": "BIM Coordinator (Tekla Software)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Design & drafting of C&S/CSA layout, section details, space management planning and plant room details.</li><li>Knowledge with Tekla structures is a must for Civil projects</li><li>Responsible for preparation of shop drawings, and As-Built drawings using Revit and CAD software.</li><li>Obtain relevant information from architectural drawings, structural, other discipline drawings.</li><li>To assist Project Manager/ Engineers on coordination, planning and visiting job sites/meetings when necessary.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Diploma/NITEC in Engineering, Architecture or related studies</li><li>At least 1-3 years of working experiences in BIM functions (ideally from C&S/CSA Trade/Discipline)</li><li>Tekla experience essential</li></ul><p>If the role resonates with you and your professional experience complements the responsibilities listed, send your resume to<strong> koh.dickson@bayesrecruitment.com</strong><br /><br />Dickson Koh, EA Registration R1103367<br />www.bayesrecruitment.com</p>",
